{"tid":1296093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"留意到有幾個POST都指林鄭有上連登 收皮喇","createTime":"2019-07-08T09:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T12:41:26.000Z","uid":69525,"like":105,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e5cf52f7c70453ce816a2d6fee6ba901f26a747f","tid":1296093,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:00:14.000Z","msg":"留意到今日有幾個POST都指林鄭有上連登<br />\n又想玩公關show啊?<br />\n<br />\n林鄭如果你真係有睇連登既話<br />\n應該好清楚所有人既五大訴求<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">一、徹底撤回修例\n二、收回暴動定義\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選</code></pre><br />\n以上五個訴求 你只需答YES/NO，答應/唔答應就得，唔好係到放曬風聲玩公關show 扮有上討論區睇民意。<br />\n依家市民要既野 唔係你出黎講兩句 話有聽民意就夠。五大訴求 唔需要討論 已經清清楚楚咁列明，唔該正式答應左先再扮交流喇 柒婆。<br />\n<br />\n另外，Babykingdom同香討先係屬於香港人既討論區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林鄭你係咪收錯風啊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f58533bb3ef230e738f6001155d29315f870fde","tid":1296093,"uid":90692,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:06:28.000Z","msg":"做得好衰既show ,. 因為佢聽日出嚟講嘢吖嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b0c150b8c4c9269a718a8bb5b72e83a859bb1e","tid":1296093,"uid":69525,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:08:04.000Z","msg":"推 聽日臨開記召<br />\n依家扮公關show啊？"},{"pid":"22b069de13408dbd690a6824fbf712367a1ac7bf","tid":1296093,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:09:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cebde8fa185ce18a71ccbe0ad9b986d6d2dc58f","tid":1296093,"uid":69525,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:15:04.00